A Saudi Arabian court sentenced a
34-year-old Saudi man to 2,000 lashes and eight years in prison
for blackmailing 13 women,  Arab News  reported, citing a Jeddah
court decision.  The man was fined 300,000 riyals ($80,000) for threatening
to publish personal pictures of his victims if he didnâ€™t get a
payment of 1,500 riyals a month from each woman, the newspaper
reported. The defendant was reported to the authorities by his
